<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Do you, too, agree that, in the book, Mia seems careless and aloof after the car crash while looking at her dead parents and unconscious self? I understand that this was supposed to depict Mia's "ghostly" state of numbness but it seemed a bit extreme that she had no feeling at all. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
