<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer10648950661819761195">Award-winning author and journalist Gayle Forman has written several bestselling novels for young adults, including the Just One Series, I Was Here, Where She Went and the #1 New York Times bestseller If I Stay, which has been translated into more than 40 languages and in 2014 was adapted into a major motion picture. <br/><br/>Gayle published Leave Me, her first novel starring adults in 2016 and her latest </span>
  <span id="freeText10648950661819761195" style="display:none">Award-winning author and journalist Gayle Forman has written several bestselling novels for young adults, including the Just One Series, I Was Here, Where She Went and the #1 New York Times bestseller If I Stay, which has been translated into more than 40 languages and in 2014 was adapted into a major motion picture. <br /><br />Gayle published Leave Me, her first novel starring adults in 2016 and her latest novel, I Have Lost My Way, comes out in March of 2018. <br /><br /><br />Gayle lives with her husband and daughters in Brooklyn.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10648950661819761195" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
